  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In fact, in the last years of school, before matric, you no longer have a teacher who is in charge of your class.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You're being taught by university professors who come and teach their subject.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They don't know your name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They take no-- they're not interested in you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Only if you are particularly outstanding and show talent do they take a personal interest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you're only allowed to write your-- what in French is called composition-- it's your tests, provided you have attended a given number of lectures in that subject since the last test was written.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it was not personal at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it's very intense, the education.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No sports at all, except I think we went swimming once a week or twice a week.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't want to exaggerate, but that-- that-- and that was not in the school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had to go out for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The exercise consisted of going round the courtyard in the morning after breakfast and in the evening after dinner.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in the free period, we could play a type of baseball game [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But that was basically-- we didn't even have a gym, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] time for gymnastics.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But you got, I think it was, two weekends off a-- a month, provided you had no bad marks against you during the previous period.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The first punishment if you did something wrong was if you were late for class, and then your weekend was canceled.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Thursday afternoon-- either Wednesday or Thursday-- Thursday afternoon, there was no school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that time was spent in the museums.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
